data.description: Looking to downsize? Add to or start your investment property portfolio? Here you go! Cozy 2 bedroom near all Indianola amenities. Hardwood floors in living room & bedrooms, kitchen will include refrigerator & stove. Full bath with laundry located in LL (washer/dryer included). 2 car garage (brand new roof & automatic opener) is a surprise at this price plus it is extra deep (20x24). Yard is mostly fenced & includes a concrete patio with space for the grill & entertaining. Vinyl siding and windows were replaced in 2011. HWH new in 2022. Another perk...close to Hy Vee, Walgreens and Moats Park on the north side of town. HSA Home warranty included. Sold AS-IS.
